title: Transformers Beast Wars Neo - 7. Duel in the Midst of Labyrinth
description:
Transformers Beast Wars Neo 7 - Duel in the Midst of the Labrinth 

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Saberback is on a solo mission which seems be be done as soon as Big Convoy and his Maximal team arrives! The only thing is, he's lost! Break, Cohrada, and Stampy are sent to get the Angolmois energy capsule but have to make there way though the mined out planet P-10908. Will the Maximals get the capsule? Or will Saberback score one for the Destrons?
